#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Units"
msgstr "Enote"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the default unit that will be used in your slides."
msgstr "Izberite privzeto enoto, ki bo uporabljena v prosojnicah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handle radius"
msgstr "Polmer ročaja"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a shape with the default tool (arrow) you see the yellow and "
"red rectangles. These are called handles (used for resizing, rotation, ...). "
"The handle radius changes the size of the handles. If you make them bigger "
"it is easier to hit them."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete obliko s privzetim orodjem (puščica), vidite rumene in rdeče "
"pravokotnike. Imenujejo se ročaji (uporabljajo se za spreminjanje velikosti, "
"vrtenje, ...). Polmer ročaja spremeni velikost ročajev. Če jih povečate, jih "
"boste lažje udarili."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grab sensitivity"
msgstr "Občutljivost grabljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option defines how exactly you need to hit a handle to select it."
msgstr "Ta možnost določa, kako natančno morate zadeti ročaj, da ga izberete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste offset"
msgstr "Zamik lepljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is only active if <guilabel>Paste at Cursor</guilabel> is disabled. If "
"you copy a shape with the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> and paste it with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>, and do that at a place where already "
"a shape is this offset is used to paste the new shape to the bottom/right."
msgstr ""
"To je aktivno le, če je onemogočeno <guilabel>Prilepi ob kazalec</guilabel>. "
"Če kopirate obliko z bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> in jo prilepite z <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> in to naredite na mestu, kjer je že oblika, ta "
"odmik se uporabi za lepljenje nove oblike spodaj/desno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste at Cursor"
msgstr "Prilepi na kazalec"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disables the paste offset and insert a pasted shape at the mouse cursor "
"position."
msgstr ""
"Onemogoči odmik lepljenja in vstavi prilepljeno obliko na položaj miškinega "
"kazalca."

#. Tag: title
#: options.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Grid</title>"
msgstr "<title>Mreža</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: options.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Grid</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mreža</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: options.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Grid</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mreža</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Grid</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Mreža</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show grid"
msgstr "Pokaži mrežo"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &stage; will display a grid of dots representing the "
"intersections of imaginary horizontal and vertical lines. You can use these "
"dots to precisely position objects on the slide."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, bo &stage; prikazal mrežo pik, ki predstavljajo presečišča "
"namišljenih vodoravnih in navpičnih črt. S temi pikami lahko natančno "
"postavite predmete na prosojnico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Snap to grid"
msgstr "Pripni na mrežo"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is enabled, when dropping or moving objects on the slide the top "
"left corner of the object will <quote>snap</quote> or move, to the nearest "
"grid point."
msgstr ""
"Če je to omogočeno, se pri spuščanju ali premikanju predmetov na prosojnici "
"zgornji levi kot predmeta <quote>zaskoči</quote> ali premakne na najbližjo "
"točko mreže."

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This does reduce your freedom to freely position objects on the slide, "
"however it also helps to line up objects precisely. It is easily disabled or "
"enabled with this option, allowing you the best of both worlds."
msgstr ""
"To sicer zmanjšuje vašo svobodo pri prostem postavljanju predmetov na "
"prosojnico, vendar pomaga tudi pri natančnem razvrščanju predmetov. S to "
"možnostjo ga je enostavno onemogočiti ali omogočiti, kar vam omogoča "
"najboljše iz obeh svetov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grid color:"
msgstr "Barva mreže:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can change here the grid color which is black as default."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko spremenite barvo mreže, ki je privzeto črna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spacing"
msgstr "Razmik"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to keep the same ratio for the two settings below by having "
"the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"link.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon or to separate the two "
"settings by using the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"break.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, da ohranite enako razmerje za spodnji dve nastavitvi, tako "
"da imate ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"link.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ali ločite dve "
"nastavitvi z uporabo ikone <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"break.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontal:"
msgstr "Vodoravno:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the space in centimeters between two points on an horizontal line on the "
"grid. Default is 0.5 centimeter."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite razmik v centimetrih med dvema točkama na vodoravni črti na mreži. "
"Privzeta vrednost je 0,5 centimetra."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical:"
msgstr "Navpično:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the space in centimeters between two points on a vertical line on the "
"grid. Default is 0.5 centimeter."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite razmik v centimetrih med dvema točkama na navpični črti na mreži. "
"Privzeta vrednost je 0,5 centimetra."

